{{Infobox journal | title = Estudios filológicos | cover = | discipline = [[Linguistic]]s, [[literature]] | abbreviation = | editor = | language = English, Spanish | publisher = [[Southern University of Chile]] | country = Chile | history = 2010-present | frequency = Biannual | website = http://www.scielo.cl/revistas/efilolo/eaboutj.htm | link1 = | link1-name = | ISSN = 0071-1713 | eISSN = 0717-6171 | OCLC = 473758173 }} '''''Estudios filológicos''''' is an [[academic journal]] published by the Humanities and Philosophy Faculty of the [[Southern University of Chile]]. It covers a wide range of [[linguistic]]s and [[literature]]-related topics, primarily on issues that are relevant to [[Iberoamerica]].
