{{Infobox language |name=Serudung Murut |nativename=Tidong |states=[[Indonesia]], [[Malaysia]] |region=[[Borneo]] |ethnicity=1,000 [[Tidung people]] (2015)<ref name=e19/> |speakers=400|date=2015|ref=e19 |familycolor=Austronesian |fam2=[[Malayo-Polynesian languages|Malayo-Polynesian]] |fam3=[[North Bornean languages|North Bornean]] |fam4=[[Southwest Sabahan languages|Southwest Sabahan]] |fam5=[[Paitanic languages|Paitanic]] |iso3=srk |glotto=seru1246 |glottorefname=Serudung Murut |script=Unwritten }}
'''Serudung Murut''', or '''Serudung''', is one of several [[Sabahan language]] of [[Borneo]] spoken by the [[Tidong people]].
